title: From Misfit to Hypocrite - H3H3productions' story (Ethan Klein)

media:group.media:title: From Misfit to Hypocrite - H3H3productions' story (Ethan Klein)
media:group.media:description:
Ethan Klein and Hila Klein have done much for the community as beyond setting a standard for modern commentary they have defended fair use in the court of law for all creators that use YouTube. But as their revenue was waning and looking for a way to survive they focused on creating podcast content in place of commentary videos which is where the problems begin...
